io.servicetalk.http.api

Interface HttpDeserializer<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of objects to deserialize.

    public interface HttpDeserializer<T>
    A factory to address deserialization concerns for HTTP request/response payload bodies.

    • Method Detail

      • deserialize

        T deserialize(HttpHeaders headers,
              Buffer payload)
        Deserialize a single Object into a T.
        Parameters:
        headers - The HttpHeaders associated with the payload.
        payload - The Object to deserialize. The contents are assumed to be in memory, otherwise this method may block.
        Returns:
        The result of the deserialization.

      • deserialize

        BlockingIterable<T> deserialize(HttpHeaders headers,
                                BlockingIterable<Buffer> payload)
        Deserialize a BlockingIterable of Objects into a BlockingIterable of type T.
        Parameters:
        headers - The HttpHeaders associated with the payload.
        payload - Provides the Objects to deserialize. The contents are assumed to be in memory, otherwise this method may block.
        Returns:
        a BlockingIterable of type T which is the result of the deserialization.

        payload - Provides the Objects to deserialize.
        Returns:
        a Publisher of type T which is the result of the deserialization.
